Class SLF4JLog

java.lang.Object
  quickfix.SLF4JLog
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Log
public class SLF4JLog
extends Object

A Log using the SLF4J wrapper that supports JDK 1.4 logging, Log4J and others. This log should be created using the associated factory.

See Also:
SLF4JLogFactory
